Champion Training Routine – 4.5 hours
  First read a Guide from a player that you trust – 10 minutes
  Read EVERYTHING on the wiki page – 10 minutes
  Watch a Video/Stream about the champion – 30 minutes to 1 hour
  Go through 2 mechanics trainings with the champion – 10 minutes
  Play 3 Normal Games and try to emulate what you saw in the video/stream – 3 hours
    How do I lane with this champion
    How do I build this champion
    What is this champion’s role in team fights
    Should I try to team fight with this champion
    When are this champion’s power spikes
